## Input objects

The following objects are assumed to be in the workspace from the upstream
microbiome and diet pipelines:

-   `dist_mithun`, `dist_mithun_fam` — microbiome Aitchison distance matrices
    (ASV-level and Family-level).
-   `physeq_diet.clr.ind.dist`, `dist_diet` — diet Aitchison distance
    matrices.
-   `physeq_mithun.fix.family`, `physeq_diet.clr` — CLR-transformed phyloseq
    objects.
-   `physeq_mithun.meta` — sample metadata for mithun (with `SampleID`,
    `Season`, `Ind`).
-   `alpha_diversity.` — mithun alpha-diversity table (with `Shannon`,
    `Observed`, `Season`).
-   `diet.physeq_diet.rich` — diet alpha-diversity table.

```{r aliases}
# Convenience aliases used below

diet_asv_dist       <- physeq_diet.clr.ind.dist
microbiome_asv_dist <- dist_mithun
```

